our lending delinquency and write-off rates and growth of provision expense being higher than current expectations, which will depend in part on changes in the level of loan
balances, delinquency rates, mix of loan balances, loans related to new card members and other borrowers performing as expected, unemployment rates, the volume of bankruptcies and recoveries of previously
